      "seed": 1856803318,
      "version": 1365,
      "versionNonce": 1841091574,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1782900051411,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "For agent engineering, we need to understand that, any\ninteraction between different components could be failed, which\nrequire to handle carefully.\n\n1. Connection problem\n   - timeout\n   - rejection\n2. Result unexpected\n   - upgrade with incompatability\n\n\nFor system efficiency, we need to provide the fitting context as\nprecise as possible.\n",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "jrUybrUAAiOlDRbrDcPlM",
      "originalText": "For agent engineering, we need to understand that, any interaction between different components could be failed, which require to handle carefully.\n\n1. Connection problem\n   - timeout\n   - rejection\n2. Result unexpected\n   - upgrade with incompatability\n\n\nFor system efficiency, we need to provide the fitting context as precise as possible.\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
